OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPlanned job cuts fall      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdespite furlough deadline  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, August saw the lowest figure for       
OL,6, proposed job cuts for seven years,     
OL,7, despite the imminent end of the        
OL,8, government's furlough scheme.          
OL,10,FFigures published by the Insolvency    
OL,11,FService show that British employers    
OL,12,Fplanned 12,687 job cuts in August, a   
OL,13,Ffall of 11% since July.                
OL,15,FThe data suggests that the predicted   
OL,16,Fsurge in unemployment this autumn may  
OL,17,Fbe smaller than expected.              
OL,19,FAt the height of the pandemic, firms   
OL,20,Fproposed over 150,000 job cuts a month.
